  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "アーケードゲーム「アルカノイド」の続編です。パドルを使ってボールを動かし、ブロックを打ち当ててレベルをクリアしましょう。現在のレベルのブロックがすべて消えたら、次のレベルに進みます。レーザーやパドルの長さを伸ばすなどのパワーアップが、レベル中にあなたを助けてくれます。アーケード版とは異なり、続編にはボスバトルやストーリー性もあります。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Much like the game Breakout, the player controls the \"Vaus\", a space vessel that acts as the game's \"paddle\" which prevents a ball from falling from the playing field, attempting to bounce it against a number of bricks. The ball striking a brick causes the brick to disappear. When all the bricks are gone, the player goes to the next level, where another pattern of bricks appear. There are a number of variations (bricks that have to be hit multiple times, flying enemy ships, etc.) and power-up capsules to enhance the Vaus (expand the Vaus, multiply the number of balls, equip a laser cannon, break directly to the next level, etc.), but the gameplay remains the same.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
